author: Al Jazeera
title: Asia passes on coronavirus lessons
description: What the rest of the world is learning from how parts of Asia handled the initial virus outbreak.
content:
Many of the coronavirus measures that have been adopted by affected countries were introduced weeks ago in East Asia.
